	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Almost certainly a military tribune in the consilium of L. Cornelius Lentulus Crus (217). Cos. 49, in Asia in 49, since he is named in Josephus' list (AJ 14.229, 238) between two military tribunes so specifically termed (J. Suolahti, Arctos 2, 1958, 152-166).[58x]\n" .
